name: la noche
description:
The night tends to scare people
who are too used to the light

It's the night
That brings us 
Silence
Contemplation
temporary death
and dreams
in which the deceased ones
come sometimes 
saying a word or two

The night gives a chance 
for darkness to visit
a chance for us to see the stars
a chance sometimes we missed
due too much twinkles and drink

When a day is too bright for some
The night is always there
ready to enfold us 
in her solemn embrace


- 4000x6000
- 300 DPI
